<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/edward-g-bulwer-lytton-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_117841 oncl_a" title="view author">Edward G. Bulwer-Lytton</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_42" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/jacqueline_bisset_130070?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_130070 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Character contributes to beauty. It fortifies a woman as her youth fades. A mode of conduct, a standard of courage, discipline, fortitude, and integrity can do a great deal to make a woman beautiful.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/jacqueline-bisset-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_130070 oncl_a" title="view author">Jacqueline Bisset</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_43" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/joseph_b_wirthlin_645827?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_645827 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
The more often we see the things around us - even the beautiful and wonderful things - the more they become invisible to us. That is why we often take for granted the beauty of this world: the flowers, the trees, the birds, the clouds - even those we love. Because we see things so often, we see them less and less.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/joseph-b-wirthlin-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_645827 oncl_a" title="view author">Joseph B. Wirthlin</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_44" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/juvenal_117830?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_117830 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Rare is the union of beauty and purity.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/juvenal-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_117830 oncl_a" title="view author">Juvenal</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_45" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/maya_angelou_132707?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_132707 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
It is time for parents to teach young people early on that in diversity there is beauty and there is strength.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/maya-angelou-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_132707 oncl_a" title="view author">Maya Angelou</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_46" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<div class="qti-listm">
<a title="view quote" href="/quotes/edgar_allan_poe_142622?src=t_beauty" class="oncl_q"> <img id="qimage_142622" src="/photos_tr/en/e/edgarallanpoe/142622/edgarallanpoe1.jpg?v=4" class="bqphtgrid" alt="Beauty of whatever kind, in its supreme development, invariably excites the sensitive soul to tears. - Edgar Allan Poe" loading="lazy" width=600 height=315></a>
</div>
<a href="/quotes/edgar_allan_poe_142622?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_142622 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Beauty of whatever kind, in its supreme development, invariably excites the sensitive soul to tears.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/edgar-allan-poe-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_142622 oncl_a" title="view author">Edgar Allan Poe</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_47" class="m-ad-brick grid-item m-ad-minh boxy-ad">
<div id="div-gpt-ad-1418667263920-3-mult_auct6_edge" class="mbl_qtbox bq_300x250_edge ">
<div id="div-gpt-ad-1418667263920-3-mult_auct6" class="bq_ad_square_multi bqAdCollapse "></div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_48" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/aristotle_117836?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_117836 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Personal beauty is a greater recommendation than any letter of reference.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/aristotle-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_117836 oncl_a" title="view author">Aristotle</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_49" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/albert_camus_117821?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_117821 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Beauty is unbearable, drives us to despair, offering us for a minute the glimpse of an eternity that we should like to stretch out over the whole of time.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/albert-camus-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_117821 oncl_a" title="view author">Albert Camus</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_50" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/ivana_trump_176251?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_176251 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Gorgeous hair is the best revenge.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/ivana-trump-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_176251 oncl_a" title="view author">Ivana Trump</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_51" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/aldous_huxley_118983?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_118983 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Beauty is worse than wine, it intoxicates both the holder and beholder.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/aldous-huxley-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_118983 oncl_a" title="view author">Aldous Huxley</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_52" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/david_hume_161079?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_161079 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Beauty in things exists in the mind which contemplates them.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/david-hume-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_161079 oncl_a" title="view author">David Hume</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_53" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/ovid_397651?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_397651 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Beauty is a fragile gift.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/ovid-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_397651 oncl_a" title="view author">Ovid</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_54" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/alicia_machado_359296?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_359296 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Beauty is only temporary, but your mind lasts you a lifetime.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/alicia-machado-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_359296 oncl_a" title="view author">Alicia Machado</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_55" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<div class="qti-listm">
<a title="view quote" href="/quotes/leo_tolstoy_104250?src=t_beauty" class="oncl_q"> <img id="qimage_104250" src="/photos_tr/en/l/leotolstoy/104250/leotolstoy1.jpg?v=4" class="bqphtgrid" alt="It is amazing how complete is the delusion that beauty is goodness. - Leo Tolstoy" loading="lazy" width=600 height=315></a>
</div>
<a href="/quotes/leo_tolstoy_104250?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_104250 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
It is amazing how complete is the delusion that beauty is goodness.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/leo-tolstoy-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_104250 oncl_a" title="view author">Leo Tolstoy</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_56" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/emily_dickinson_154095?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_154095 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Beauty is not caused. It is.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/emily-dickinson-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_154095 oncl_a" title="view author">Emily Dickinson</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_57" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/william_butler_yeats_108900?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_108900 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
I heard the old, old, men say &#39;all that&#39;s beautiful drifts away, like the waters.&#39;
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/william-butler-yeats-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_108900 oncl_a" title="view author">William Butler Yeats</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_58" class="m-ad-brick grid-item m-ad-minh boxy-ad">
<div id="div-gpt-ad-1418667263920-2-mult_auct7_edge" class="mbl_qtbox bq_300x250_edge ">
<div id="div-gpt-ad-1418667263920-2-mult_auct7" class="bq_ad_square_multi bqAdCollapse "></div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_59" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/george_meredith_382361?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_382361 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
A witty woman is a treasure; a witty beauty is a power.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/george-meredith-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_382361 oncl_a" title="view author">George Meredith</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_60" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/priscilla_presley_275382?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_275382 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Inner beauty should be the most important part of improving one&#39;s self.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/priscilla-presley-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_275382 oncl_a" title="view author">Priscilla Presley</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_61" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/socrates_117827?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_117827 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Beauty is a short-lived tyranny.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/socrates-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_117827 oncl_a" title="view author">Socrates</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_62" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/karl_wilhelm_friedrich_sc_388467?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_388467 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Beauty is that which is simultaneously attractive and sublime.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/karl-wilhelm-friedrich-sc-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_388467 oncl_a" title="view author">Karl Wilhelm Friedrich Schlegel</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_63" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/rosalind_russell_104266?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_104266 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Taking joy in living is a woman&#39;s best cosmetic.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/rosalind-russell-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_104266 oncl_a" title="view author">Rosalind Russell</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_64" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<div class="qti-listm">
<a title="view quote" href="/quotes/munshi_premchand_184150?src=t_beauty" class="oncl_q"> <img id="qimage_184150" src="/photos_tr/en/m/munshipremchand/184150/munshipremchand1.jpg?v=4" class="bqphtgrid" alt="Beauty doesn&#39;t need ornaments. Softness can&#39;t bear the weight of ornaments. - Munshi Premchand" loading="lazy" width=600 height=315></a>
</div>
<a href="/quotes/munshi_premchand_184150?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_184150 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Beauty doesn&#39;t need ornaments. Softness can&#39;t bear the weight of ornaments.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/munshi-premchand-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_184150 oncl_a" title="view author">Munshi Premchand</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_65" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/havelock_ellis_164058?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_164058 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
The absence of flaw in beauty is itself a flaw.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/havelock-ellis-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_164058 oncl_a" title="view author">Havelock Ellis</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_66" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/clara_schumann_314803?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_314803 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Why hurry over beautiful things? Why not linger and enjoy them?
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/clara-schumann-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_314803 oncl_a" title="view author">Clara Schumann</a>
</div>
<div id="pos_1_67" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/laurence_j_peter_108546?src=t_beauty" class="b-qt qt_108546 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
Every girl should use what Mother Nature gave her before Father Time takes it away.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/laurence-j-peter-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_108546 oncl_a" title="view author">Laurence J. Peter</a>
</div>
</div>
